(September 12, 1961)

In decisions Nos. 1-5 the court is as follows: Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, Eager and Noonan, JJ.

William A. White & Sons v. Seymour Scott.

Motion for an extension of time to serve an answer to the complaint granted upon the terms and conditions contained in the order to show cause, dated June 22, 1961.
